... in every Ket[<|...|>] appearing in expr. KetSort[expr] applies to every \
species involved in expr. When expr involves Ket[...] for unlabelled qubits, \
it applies Sort[Ket[...]] to every Ket[...] in expr.", "synonyms" -> {}, 
